data.meta_description: Ping Security offers security professional services and have a wide selection of security vendors. We service enterprise, small to midsize businesses.

About Us

Shaw Business has the scale to meet connectivity solutions now and into the future with a Fibre network of over a million kilometers, top tier-speeds and enterprise grade technology. Shaw Business offers a multitude of solutions including, Broadband Internet, Data, SD WAN, Voice and TV.

Whether it’s a reliable Internet connection for direct payment transactions or incredible speed for day-to-day file transfers, count on Shaw Business to deliver what you need, when you need it. Shaw Business provides industry leading speeds, a superior network with a plan for any size business, dependable connections, and unlimited data.
